{c_label}Cooldown:{/c} {c_resource}{Cooldown Time}{/c} seconds
Subo tosses an incendiary at an enemy, dealing {if:SF_17}{c_number}{payload:IMPACT_PAYLOAD}{/c}{else}minor{/if} Physical damage and Stunning them for {c_number}[{buffduration:STUN_BUFF}|1|]{/c} |4second;seconds before exploding into flames. For the next {c_number}{SF_4}{/c} seconds, enemies within the area repeatedly take {if:SF_17}{c_number}{dot:BURN_BUFF}{/c}{else}light{/if} Burning damage over {c_number}{SF_7}{/c} seconds.

Selecting a Mercenary Core Skill alters their wielded Weapon and Basic Attack.
{c_label}Weapon:{/c} {c_important}Crossbow{/c}
{c_label}Basic Attack:{/c} {c_important}Salvo{/c}
Subo launches {c_number}{SF_16}{/c} bolts at an enemy, each dealing {if:SF_17}{c_number}{payload:MELEE_PAYLOAD_TOOLTIP}{/c}{else}light{/if} Physical damage. The final bolt explodes, Slowing enemies by {c_number}[{SF_13}*100|%|]{/c} for {c_number}{SF_14}{/c} seconds.
